{"view":"article","slug":"pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell","category":"Pyraminx","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Pyraminx","title":{"en":"Pyraminx Oka Method"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Pyraminx Oka Method</strong></p><p><strong>Start</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>On the same corner, solve one edge and make an Oka (misoriented edge in the wrong slot).</p><p><strong>Bottom Centers</strong></p><p>Similar to the correspond step in keyhole method.</p><p><strong>Oka and Keyhole</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R'\">R U R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U R\">R' U R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L R L' U' R'\">L R L' U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' L' R U L\">R' L' R U L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R' U R' U')\">(R' U R' U')</span></p><p><strong>(R U R)</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>ELL</strong></p><p>Same as the correspond step in keyhole method.</p><p><strong>Pyraminx Bell Method</strong></p><p><strong>Start开始</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>On the same corner, solve one edge and make a Bell (oriented edge in the wrong slot).</p><p><strong>Bottom Centers</strong></p><p>Similar to the correspond step in keyhole method.</p><p><strong>Bell and Keyhole</strong></p><p>S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>S</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>H</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R2' L R L' R\">R2' L R L' R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L2 R' L' R L'\">L2 R' L' R L'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L R L' U' R'\">L R L' U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' L' R U L\">R' L' R U L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S (R L R' L')\">S (R L R' L')</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>ELL</strong></p><p><a id=\"_Hlk294819\"></a>Same as the correspond step in keyhole method.</p>"},"algs":["R U R'","R' U R","L R L' U' R'","R' L' R U L","(R' U R' U')","R2' L R L' R","L2 R' L' R L'","S (R L R' L')"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-oka-bell/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
